definition: Fiji, country in the southwest Pacific Ocean
phonetic fei or fi/elegant/phi (Greek letter Φ, φ)
to cross a river/to aid or relieve/to be of help
only used in 濟濟|济济[ji3 ji3]
used in place names associated with the Ji River 濟水|济水[Ji3 Shui3]/surname Ji

sentences.english: His studies of volcanoes on the Fijian island of Kadavu indicated they had not been active for tens of thousands of years.
sentences.chinese: 他研究斐济卡达屋岛上据称几万年未活动的火山。

sentences.english: Thanks to God for bringing the missionary teams to Fiji. They did open a new page here.
sentences.chinese: 感谢神，使用团队的弟兄姊妹，为斐济展开新一页。

sentences.english: It was really the people I met on the island that made my Fijian experience unforgettable.
sentences.chinese: 在岛上所遇之人让我真正觉得这次斐济之行非常难忘。

sentences.english: It's two biggest islands are Vanua Levu and VitiLevu.
sentences.chinese: 斐济最大的两个岛屿分别是瓦努阿岛和维提岛。

sentences.english: He said that the Fijian people would always remember the friendly sentiments cherished by the Chinese people towards them.
sentences.chinese: 斐济人民珍视并将永远铭记伟大中国人民的友好情谊。

sentences.english: Li said that Fiji was the first Pacific Island country to establish diplomatic ties with China.
sentences.chinese: 李肇星表示，斐济是最早同中国建交的太平洋岛国。

sentences.english: The pathogen of this disease is belong to Reoviridae Fiji genus.
sentences.chinese: 引起该病害的病毒属于呼肠孤科斐济属。

sentences.english: Sugar is Fiji's second biggest export earner.
sentences.chinese: 糖是斐济第二大出口创汇产品。

sentences.english: I started Tribewanted on Vorovoro Island, Fiji in 2006.
sentences.chinese: 2006年，我在斐济莫多莫多岛创建了“部族客”。

sentences.english: Fiji was probably the nicest that I went to surf-wise.
sentences.chinese: 以冲浪来说，斐济大概是我去过最好的。

sentences.english: Fiji, a multi-ethnic nation, has undergone tremendous social transformation in recent years.
sentences.chinese: 多民族国家斐济近年来经历了巨大的社会变迁。

sentences.english: Take off your coat and let's go to Republic of Fiji for vacation.
sentences.chinese: 走吧，脱下你的衣裳，和我一起去斐济旅行吧。

sentences.english: Roundtrip Economy class air ticket for Hong Kong and Fiji on CX.
sentences.chinese: 国泰航空公司来回香港至斐济机票。

sentences.english: Iloilovatu said that the Fijian people hold friendly feelings towards China.
sentences.chinese: 伊洛伊洛说，斐济人民对中国怀有友好的感情。

sentences.english: World's first undersea resort located on a private island in Fiji.
sentences.chinese: 位于斐济某私人海岛上的世界第一所海下酒店。
